biography: Dr. Darina Goldin has a Ph.D. in Control Science, but secretly wishes she had pursued a degree in pure math instead. Either way, she'd probably still have ended up as a principal data scientist at Bayes Esports, where she has been modeling Esports Data for the past 8 years. When not at her desk, Darina can be found on the mats competing in Brazillian Jiu-Jitsu.
